(6, 'Sergio Barreto', 'Defensor', 'Nacido en Clorinda, Formosa.', '1999-04-24', 1.83, 'https://clubaindependiente.com.ar/img/plantel/barreto.jpg', '<p><strong style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">Sergio Dami&aacute;n Barreto</strong><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">est&aacute; naturalizado paraguayo. Juega como defensor en&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Club Atl&eacute;tico Independiente\" href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Club_Atl%C3%A9tico_Independiente\">Independiente</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">, de la&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Primera Divisi&oacute;n de Argentina\" href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primera_Divisi%C3%B3n_de_Argentina\">Liga Profesional</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">.</span><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference separada\" style=\"line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: 0.6ch; color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\"></sup></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">Lleg&oacute; al club con apenas 9 a&ntilde;os, en 2008.&nbsp;</span><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference separada\" style=\"line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: 0.6ch; color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background: none;