(9, 'Fernando Da Rosa', 'Defensor', 'Nacido en Argentina.', '2001-04-02', 1.81, 'https://clubaindependiente.com.ar/img/plantel/2023/placas_web_11.jpg', '<p><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Fernando Sebasti&aacute;n Da Sosa</strong><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">, es futbolista de Argentina y se desempe&ntilde;a como Defensor en Independiente.</span></p>', 1),
(10, 'Patricio Javier Ostachuk', 'Defensor', 'Nacido en Oberá, Misiones.', '2000-05-05', 1.81, 'https://clubaindependiente.com.ar/img/plantel/ostachuk.jpg', '<p><strong style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">Javier Patricio Ostachuk</strong><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;(nacido el 5 de mayo de 2000) es un futbolista profesional&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Asociaci&oacute;n de Futbol\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Association_football\">argentino</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;que juega como&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Defensor (f&uacute;tbol de asociaci&oacute;n)\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Defender_(association_football)#Centre-back\">central</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;en&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Club Atl&eacute;tico Independiente\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Club_Atl%C3%A9tico_Independiente\">Independiente</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">Comenz&oacute; su carrera juvenil como&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"centrocampista\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Midfielder\">centrocampista</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;en 2004, con cuatro a&ntilde;os, en el Olimpia de Ober&aacute;;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">que luego se conocer&iacute;a como Olimpia / San Antonio despu&eacute;s de una fusi&oacute;n.</span></span><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;En 2014, Ostachuk tuvo una serie de pruebas con&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Newell&acute;s Old Boys\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Newell%27s_Old_Boys\">Newell\'s Old Boys</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;, quienes lo fichar&iacute;an en 2015.&nbsp;</span><sup id=\"cite_ref-DM2_6-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px; color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\"></sup><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">Sin embargo, Ostachuk permaneci&oacute; en Newell\'s solo un a&ntilde;o antes de partir.&nbsp;</span><sup id=\"cite_ref-DM1_3-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px; color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\"></sup><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">2016 vio a Ostachuk, luego de un juicio, unirse a&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Club_Atl%C3%A9tico_Independiente\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Independiente</span></a>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">Hizo el gran avance en el f&uacute;tbol del primer equipo en 2020, despu&eacute;s de haber hecho la transici&oacute;n a un&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Defensor (f&uacute;tbol de asociaci&oacute;n)\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Defender_(association_football)#Centre-back\">central</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;en los a&ntilde;os anteriores.</span><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Ostachuk hizo su debut el 6 de Diciembre de 2020 en la&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"2020 Copa de la Liga Profesional\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_Copa_de_la_Liga_Profesional\">Copa de la Liga Profesional</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;con victoria frente a&nbsp;</span><a