-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">El debut absoluto de Costa se produjo el 6 de diciembre de 2020 en una&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">victoria&nbsp;</span></span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Copa de la Liga Profesional 2020\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_Copa_de_la_Liga_Profesional\">de Copa de la Liga Profesional sobre&nbsp;</a><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"Defensa y Justicia\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Defensa_y_Justicia\">Defensa y Justicia</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;, ya que jug&oacute; ochenta y ocho minutos antes de ser sustituido por&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0645ad; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: sans-serif;\" title=\"patricio ostachuk\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patricio_Ostachuk\">Patricio Ostachuk</a><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">.&nbsp;</span><sup id=\"cite_ref-FARV1_10-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px; color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif;\"></sup><span style=\"color: #202122; font-family: sans-serif; vertical-align: inherit;\">Escribi&oacute; los t&eacute;rminos de un contrato hasta diciembre de 2022 el 15 de diciembre de 2020.</span></p>', 1);
